        <updateDate>2019-08-05T18:05:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ensuring Patient Access to Critical Breakthrough Products Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill (1) allows designated medical breakthrough devices to be temporarily covered under Medicare during a specified transitional period, (2) establishes a process to allow for continued coverage after the transitional period has expired, and (3) modifies other Medicare payment systems relating to new medical technology. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
